About

Not separate.
Integrated.

I operate at the edge where rigorous technical systems thinking meets expressive creative practice. As a GenAI Architect, I design agentic systems that behave reliably under pressure — diagnosing silent failures, scoring trajectories, building the observability scaffolding that makes AI trustworthy.

As an artist and founder, I build Aura by Shivangi — live painting experiences, original art prints, meditation, and sound — practices that return people to presence. Both ask the same question: what does it mean to build something that truly works?

I'm also passionate about empowering women in technology — creating a global platform for learning, collaboration, and professional growth.
